<body>
  <div id="wrap">

      <%= render partial: "header_menu" %>

      <%= image_tag("ball.jpg", :alt => "golf ball", :class=>"img-responsive img-banner hidden-xs") %>

      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <h1>Our Story</h1>
            <div>As passionate golfers we wanted to bring organizing and playing in tournaments into one easy to use, golfer friendly environment. Established in 2016 Golf Stuff is a new and improved tool built for the golfing community</div>
            <h1>Features</h1>
            <div>Golf Stuff allows you to create and organize golf tournaments in just a few simple steps.</div>
            <a href="/tournaments/new"><button class="button_new button btn-home">Create Tournament</button></a>
            <div>Golf Stuff allows users to view and sign up to play or sponsor public golf tournaments. We offer secure payment through PayPal </div>
            <a href="/tournaments"><button class="button_new button">View Tournaments</button></a>
          
            <h1>Contact Us</h1>
            <h4>Phone:</h4>
            <div>+1 234 5678</div>
            <h4>Email:</h4>
            <div>admin@golfstuff.com</div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-sm-8">
                <h1>Welcome To Golf Stuff</h1>
                <div>Golf Stuff lets you browse, register, sponsor and create your own golf tournaments.</div>

                <h1>Some Upcoming Events</h1>
                <table class="table main-table">
                <tr>       

                  <th>Name</th>
                  <th>Location</th>
                  <th>Date</th>
                  <th></th>
                </tr>
                <% @tournaments.each do |t| %>
                  <tr>
                      <td><%= t.name %></td>
                      <% if !t.golf_course_id.nil?%>
                        <% @gf = GolfCourse.find(t.golf_course_id)%>
                        <td><%= @gf.name %></td>
                      <% else %>
                        <td><%= t.location %></td>
                      <% end %>
                      <td><%= t.date %></td>
                      <td>
                        <%= link_to "Details", tournament_path(t), :class=>"button-small button button_new" %>
                      </td>
                  </tr>
                <% end %> 
                
              
                </table>
            <a href="/tournaments"><button class="button_new button">See More</button></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    <div id="push"></div>
  </div> <!--End of wrap-->

  <%= render "footer" %>

</body>
</html>
